{# ===================== HI, I'M CONNIE MENSER ===================== #}
{% call section(tone="alt") %}
  <div class="about-connie">
    <div class="about-connie__media">
      <img src="{{ '/assets/img/about-connie-menser.jpg' | url }}" alt="Connie Menser, Executive Director of Full Supply" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-connie__body">
      <h2 class="about-heading">Hi, I&rsquo;m Connie Menser</h2>
      <p>I know firsthand the pressures that come with being a mentor. During my time as an International Specialist with a non-profit organization, where I helped raise national leaders both overseas and in the U.S., I discovered how my confidence and understanding of my calling allowed me to live courageously in alignment with the Great Commission.</p>
      <p>Today, I&rsquo;m committed to teaching the path to spiritual growth and biblical leadership principles that shaped me into the mentor I am today and led me to found Full Supply, Inc.</p>
      <p>I believe in you, and I&rsquo;m here to help you lead with confidence and live courageously as you fulfill your God-given calling.</p>
      <p class="about-connie__sign">Connie J Menser</p>
      <p class="about-connie__role">Executive Director</p>
      <p>{{ button("Schedule A Call With Connie", scheduleUrl, variant="accent", attrs='target="_blank" rel="noopener"') }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
